metrics.visualTitle: Total de Desempregados por Ano, Trimestre, Mês e Faixa Etária

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __ScopedCoreI0 = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano],
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Trimestre],
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[QuarterNo],
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Mês],
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[MonthNo],
      'Desemprego'[Range_Idade],
      "SumTotal_Desempregados", CALCULATE(SUM('Desemprego'[Total_Desempregados]))
    )

  VAR __ScopedCoreDM0 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Trimestre],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[QuarterNo],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Mês],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[MonthNo],
          "MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Date])))
        )
      ),
      OR(
        OR(
          OR(
            OR(
              NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano])),
              NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Trimestre]))
            ),
            NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[QuarterNo]))
          ),
          NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Mês]))
        ),
        NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[MonthNo]))
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __ScopedCoreI0,
      __ScopedCoreDM0
    )

  VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

  VAR __DS0PrimaryDbCount = 
    CALCULATE(
      COUNTROWS(
        SUMMARIZE(
          __DS0Core,
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Trimestre],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[QuarterNo],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Mês],
          'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[MonthNo]
        )
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
    CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Desemprego'[Range_Idade])))

  VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
    SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
      3500,
      __DS0Core,
      [MinDate],
      [SumTotal_Desempregados],
      350,
      'Desemprego'[Range_Idade],
      ALPHABETICAL,
      ASC,
      105000,
      60
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'Desemprego'[Range_Idade])

  VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
      __DS0BodyBinnedSample,
      "ColumnIndex",
      __DS0SecondaryBase,
      'Desemprego'[Range_Idade],
      ASC
    )

EVALUATE
  ROW(
    "DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
    "DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
    "DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
    "DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
  )

EVALUATE
  __DS0SecondaryBase

ORDER BY
  'Desemprego'[Range_Idade]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano],
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[QuarterNo],
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Trimestre],
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[MonthNo],
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Mês],
  [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    VALUES('Desemprego'[Range_Idade])

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'Desemprego'[Range_Idade], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'Desemprego'[Range_Idade]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano],
      "SumTotal_Desempregados", CALCULATE(SUM('Desemprego'[Total_Desempregados])),
      "MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Date])))
    )

  VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

  VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
    SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(3500, __DS0Core, [MinDate], [SumTotal_Desempregados], 350, , ALPHABETICAL, ASC, 105000, 60)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
  'LocalDateTable_e1f9739b-c4e1-4578-a003-82b3f3195978'[Ano]
